---
title: Thai-Inspired Roasted Shrimp and Sea Bass with Coconut Milk Risotto and Roasted Veggies
description: This fusion dish combines the flavours of Thai cuisine with a classic Italian cooking technique. Coconut milk risotto unites with roasted veggies to create a beautiful base for tender sea bass and juicy shrimp.
